                "title": "Terms of Use"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "The following table lists the software products and versions affected, and the updated version available from the <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA/NVFlare\">NVIDIA/NVFlare</a> GitHub repo that includes this security update.",
